# Cypress Practical Test Framework (UI + API | BDD + POM)

This project demonstrates a Cypress automation framework setup for both **UI and API** test automation using:
- âœ… Cypress + JavaScript
- âœ… Cucumber (BDD)
- âœ… Page Object Model (POM)
- âœ… API Request Testing (Petstore Swagger)
- âœ… Screenshot/Video capture on failure
- âœ… CLI execution with reporting

