| Folder                             | Purpose                                       |
| ---------------------------------- | --------------------------------------------- |
| `e2e/ui/features/`                 | All UI BDD `.feature` files                   |
| `e2e/api/features/`                | All API `.feature` files                      |
| `step_definitions/`                | Step implementations for UI/API               |
| `pageObjects/`                     | POM files for reusable UI selectors & actions |
| `petapi.js`                        | API helper methods for Pet endpoints          |
| `screenshots/` + `videos/`         | Auto-captured on failures                     |
| `reports/` + `mochawesome-report/` | Raw & final reports                           |
| `cypress.config.js`                | Central config for Cypress and reporter       |




Install Dependencies

npm install

Run Tests:
npx cypress run --spec "cypress/e2e/ui/features/*.feature"
npx cypress run --spec "cypress/e2e/api/features/pet.feature"


Merge JSON reports
npx mochawesome-merge cypress/reports/*.json > mochawesome.json

Generate HTML report
npx marge mochawesome.json -f report -o mochawesome-report

